NAME

  **demomarkdown** - run a markdown demo


SYNOPSIS

    demomarkdown 

DESCRIPTION

    The demomarkdown command displays demomarkdown.dsmd. It's a test command
    for text wrapping and dsmd document displaying. However, since you can't 
    scroll the document, it's recommended to instead use `dsmdbrowser 
    data/demo/markdown/demomarkdown.dsmd` if you wish to view the markdown syntax
    examples. 


SEE ALSO

    demoanim, democurses, demomousetouch, dsmdbrowser